subject: Greetings.
body:

subject: Re:   Greetings.
body:
Dear Sender,

I appreciate your concern and the information you've provided. However, I must inform you that I have not participated in any lottery or award scheme in Nigeria or elsewhere. Therefore, I believe there may be a misunderstanding or mistake.

If you have any further details or need assistance with something else, feel free to contact me.

Best wishes,
Elizabeth
